    • Constructor Detail

      • KeePassHeader

        public KeePassHeader()

      • KeePassHeader

        public KeePassHeader(ByteGenerator byteGenerator)
        Initializes the header with default values and creates new random values for crypto keys.

        Default values:

        • Compression: GZIP
        • CrsAlgorithm: Salsa20
        • TransformRounds: 8000
        • Cipher: AES
